Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit holographic interface floating in a dark urban environment, showing multiple translucent document panels that morph and shapeshift into each other like liquid mercury. One panel displays a glowing durian fruit with circuit-board patterns, another shows abstract tropical fruits rendered as wireframe holograms. The panels are stacked in a cascading arrangement within a single floating frame, suggesting documents transforming without leaving their container. Rain streaks through the background, reflecting pink and cyan light off wet surfaces. Glowing data streams connect the panels like synaptic pathways, emphasizing the dynamic interchange between forms. The scene captures the essence of fluid, modular information that reshapes itself contextually within a confined digital space.
